  <!-- HANDBOOK & POLICIES -->
  <section id="handbook">
    <h2><span class="icon">üìò</span>Resident Handbook & Key Policies</h2>
    <p class="subtitle">
      This is a quick summary. Your signed lease and the WHA Resident Handbook are the official documents.
    </p>
    <div class="card-grid">
      <div class="card">
        <span class="label">Guests & Visitors</span>
        <h3>Guest Responsibilities</h3>
        <ul class="key-points">
          <li>You are responsible for the behavior of your guests at all times.</li>
          <li>Do not let anyone into the building that you do not personally know or host.</li>
          <li>Overnight guest limits and reporting requirements apply per WHA policy.</li>
          <li>Allowing banned visitors onto the property can result in lease action.</li>
        </ul>
      </div>

      <div class="card">
        <span class="label">Housekeeping</span>
        <h3>Unit Standards</h3>
        <ul class="key-points">
          <li>Units must be reasonably clean, sanitary, and free of hazards.</li>
          <li>Trash must be bagged and disposed of in designated areas.</li>
          <li>Excess clutter, blocked exits, or pest infestation can result in violations and re-inspections.</li>
        </ul>
      </div>

      <div class="card">
        <span class="label">Criminal Activity</span>
        <h3>Zero Tolerance</h3>
        <ul class="key-points">
          <li>Drug-related or violent criminal activity can lead to lease termination.</li>
          <li>Illegal activity anywhere on the property is taken seriously.</li>
          <li>Please report suspected criminal activity to 911 and the office.</li>
        </ul>
      </div>

      <div class="card">
        <span class="label">Rent & Charges</span>
        <h3>Rent & Air Conditioning</h3>
        <ul class="key-points">
          <li>Rent is due on the 1st of each month (late if not received by policy deadline).</li>
          <li>Air conditioner charges apply per month while installed.</li>
          <li>Resident-caused damage may result in repair charges.</li>
        </ul>
      </div>

      <div class="card">
        <span class="label">Inspections</span>
        <h3>Inspections & Entry</h3>
        <ul class="key-points">
          <li>Annual and special inspections are required by HUD and WHA.</li>
          <li>Reasonable notice will be given when possible, except in emergencies.</li>
          <li>Refusing entry may result in lease enforcement steps.</li>
        </ul>
      </div>

      <div class="card">
        <span class="label">Grievances</span>
        <h3>Grievance Rights</h3>
        <ul class="key-points">
          <li>You may request an informal hearing or grievance if you disagree with certain decisions.</li>
          <li>Requests must be made in writing within the time limits in the policy.</li>
        </ul>
        <div class="btn-row">
          <!-- TODO: Replace # with a grievance request form or instructions -->
          <a href="#" class="btn btn-soft">Request a Hearing</a>
        </div>
